                        "content": "An older client with peptic ulcer disease recently has been taking cimetidine. The nurse monitors the client for which most frequent central nervous system side effect of this medication?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nCimetidine is a histamine (H2)-receptor antagonist. Older clients are especially susceptible to central nervous system side effects of cimetidine. The most frequent of these is confusion. Less common central nervous system side effects include headache, dizziness, drowsiness, and hallucinations.",
                        "id": "5b64e74de064480ebaebff2b208fb27f",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "e01206a84c444140b806c9a03ec09a83",
                                "content": "I will take the cimetidine with my meals."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "0799a26b82994cd4ac28c7268affaab3",
                                "content": "I'll know the medication is working if my diarrhea stops."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "1a9ee47fcd144e92b917ba6939316e11",
                                "content": "My episodes of heartburn will decrease if the medication is effective."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "ad0ccf245f4044b98186d9d0a3e58823",
                                "content": "Taking the cimetidine with an antacid will increase its effectiveness."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "95710aacdd3748d4aaee17c2186daad4",
                                "content": "I will notify my doctor if I become depressed or anxious."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "ccce349b961948d28e2c7d103f17014e",
                                "content": "Some of my blood levels will need to be monitored closely since I also take warfarin for atrial fibrillation."
                            }
                        ],
